s_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASt1Lrdkn", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8697879, "raw_content": "Yes the president can end TPS, the *Temporary* program.  In  Mullin v. Doe by 6-3 (commies against).  Syrians and Haitians can be sent home.  The law was clearly written to bar judicial review.\n\n\nhttps://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-1083_f204.pdf\n\n\n>The TPS statute bars judicial review of non-constitutional claims.\n\n\nAnother 6-3 in Mullin v. Al Otro Lado (commies against), you don't *enter* the U.S. until you physically *enter* the U.S.\n\n\nhttps://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-5_86qd.pdf\n\n\n>An alien standing in Mexico does not \u201carriv[e] in the United States\u201d\nby attempting, and failing, to set foot in this country. An alien \u201carrives\nin the United States\u201d only when he crosses the border. The INA thus\nneither entitles an alien standing in Mexico to apply for asylum nor\nrequires an immigration officer to inspect him\n\n\n\nAnother 6-3 (commies against), in Wolford v Hawaii, it is a violation of both 2A and 14A to ban ccw holders from private property open tot he public without the prior explicit permission of the property owner.\n\n\nhttps://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/24-1046_nmio.pdf\n\n\n>Hawaii\u2019s law prohibiting licensed concealed-carry permit holders\nfrom carrying handguns on private property open to the public without\nthe property owner\u2019s express authorization violates the Second and\nFourteenth Amendments.\n\n\n\n", "author": "keeponwinning", "created": 1782398600260, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "keeponwinning", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Another series of Trump wins, 6-3 SCOTUS on TPS immigration and 2A", "last_comment_created": 1782407791942, "content": "<p>Yes the president can end TPS, the <em>Temporary</em> program.  In  Mullin v. Doe by 6-3 (commies against).  Syrians and Haitians can be sent home.  The law was clearly written to bar judicial review.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-1083_f204.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-1083_f204.pdf</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The TPS statute bars judicial review of non-constitutional claims.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Another 6-3 in Mullin v. Al Otro Lado (commies against), you don't <em>enter</em> the U.S. until you physically <em>enter</em> the U.S.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-5_86qd.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/25-5_86qd.pdf</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>An alien standing in Mexico does not \u201carriv[e] in the United States\u201d\nby attempting, and failing, to set foot in this country. An alien \u201carrives\nin the United States\u201d only when he crosses the border. The INA thus\nneither entitles an alien standing in Mexico to apply for asylum nor\nrequires an immigration officer to inspect him</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Another 6-3 (commies against), in Wolford v Hawaii, it is a violation of both 2A and 14A to ban ccw holders from private property open tot he public without the prior explicit permission of the property owner.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/24-1046_nmio.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/25pdf/24-1046_nmio.pdf</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hawaii\u2019s law prohibiting licensed concealed-carry permit holders\nfrom carrying handguns on private property open to the public without\nthe property owner\u2019s express authorization violates the Second and\nFourteenth Amendments.</p>\n</blockquote>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASt1KjFMi", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 578, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8696894, "raw_content": "", "author": "fforgotpasswordagain", "created": 1782343733436, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Lunar", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASt1KjFMi.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/Z07vlkfRur8k.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/d2zajMzyo0if8GXQ.png", "width": 683, "content-type": "png", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UNH1Y*acI@D*0gkD$itQMztRxFt7~BsmS#E1", "full_resolution": [800, 711]}, "title": "It's All So Tiresome.......", "last_comment_created": 1782405811022, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 26, "score_up": 578, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2070158027261460765", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASt1MxpTv", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8698013, "raw_content": "", "author": "PiratePatriotParrot", "creat